      <title>乌克兰称俄罗斯军队向其占领的核电站开火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-11/ukraine-says-russian-army-starts-fire-at-occupied-zaporizhzhia-nuclear-plant</link>
